Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Caesar had my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it end up in your hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He just got the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me keep your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's a deal!
